This paper focuses on the security management and automation of IoT infrastructures, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of graph-based specifications and conflict resolution, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also deals with the management of heterogeneous devices and programming interfaces, which is a common challenge in systems and control (cs.SY) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
